sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant FE as Frontend<br/>React
    participant API as FastAPI<br/>Backend
    participant LLM as AWS Bedrock<br/>Claude Sonnet
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    Note over U,DB: Text-to-SQL Chat Flow (SSE Streaming)

    U->>FE: "What's the avg charge<br/>for 93306 in Florida?"
    FE->>API: POST /api/chat<br/>{message, history[]}

    API->>API: Build prompt:<br/>schema + few-shot examples<br/>+ conversation history

    API->>LLM: Invoke with schema context
    LLM-->>API: Generated SQL:<br/>SELECT AVG(avg_submitted_charge)<br/>FROM cases WHERE hcpcs_cd='93306'<br/>AND npi IN (SELECT npi FROM<br/>providers WHERE state='FL')

    API->>API: Validate SQL<br/>(read-only, no DDL,<br/>complexity limits)
    API->>DB: Execute validated SQL
    DB-->>API: Result: {avg: 412.37}

    API->>LLM: Format response +<br/>generate chart spec

    Note over API,FE: SSE Stream begins

    loop Token streaming
        LLM-->>API: Token chunk
        API-->>FE: SSE: {token: "The average..."}
        FE-->>U: Render token
    end

    API-->>FE: SSE: {chart_spec: {<br/>type: "bar",<br/>data: [...],<br/>xKey: "state"}}
    FE-->>U: Render Recharts bar chart

    Note over U,DB: Risk Narrative Flow

    U->>FE: Click "Scan" on claim
    FE->>API: POST /api/score<br/>{npi, hcpcs, charge, volume}
    API->>DB: Lookup provider + baselines
    DB-->>API: Provider profile + peers
    API->>API: Compute signals +<br/>risk/legitimacy scores
    API->>LLM: Generate narrative from<br/>structured signal data
    LLM-->>API: "This cardiologist bills<br/>4.2x the FL peer average..."
    API-->>FE: ScoreResult {score, signals[],<br/>narrative, provenance[]}
    FE-->>U: Risk gauge + signal cards<br/>+ AI narrative
